Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Gaki no tsukai ya arahende!!\NLet's go to a town we've never been to and ask for the 5 best places there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- That was so loud, wasn't it?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- You always say my voice is too quiet or too loud.\N- That was on purpose, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's serious.\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the 2nd segment in 10 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys like this segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We had fun last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We like this kind of thing, but apparently Hamada-san doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san looks down on ordinary people.\NHe doesn't like them very much, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are we supposed to do?\N- Just like last time, these have the town's name written on them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's have Yamazaki-san, the scum of Yoshimoto, draw lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way, I can't draw lots.\NThat would be admitting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- You must not admit that.\N- Otherwise, you will become a scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,May I draw a lot that has nothing to do with this once?\NThis has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This has really nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any of this kind of luck, so it probably says a shabby place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinano-machi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shinano-machi is right there!\N- It's right there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I have no luck, right?\NI'm glad I did not draw lots.\NShinano-machi is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like a jogging trail!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after all, let's have Yamazaki-san, our scum, draw the lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please!\N- Please draw a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm a scum after all.\N- Speaking of scum, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You might draw the one that we really don't all know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to draw a town we've never been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not if it's a town someone has been to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to call you a scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iwai?\N- Iwai??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in Minami-Boso City, Chiba Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's far away there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's really far away there.\N- Minami-Boso is very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's great. Have you found it yet?\N- Here it's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How far away it's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just before Tateyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have decided the town we are going to is Iwai, Chiba Prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go to Iwai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[One week later]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well guys, we have arrived at Iwai Station on the JR Uchibo Line in Minami-Boso City, Chiba Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who drew the lots?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We had forgotten, but apparently it was Zaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you kept quiet about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rather...\N- He was trying to blame Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to blame this on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, blaming someone else for our coming to Iwai station is a problem in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From the point of view of the residents of Iwai,\N"Is this a town for punishment?"\NThey would think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is not someone's blame.\N- Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it seems this is a shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there would be something here since it's in front of the station, but there's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules are the same as last time.\NLet's ask the residents of this town for their top five recommended places around Iwai station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We will choose one of them and go to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be any place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We will get permission to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't get permission, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's not allowed to be shown on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask them from the 5th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately they started to ask them for the recommended 5th place around Iwai station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone got off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the train just stopped.\NSome young people are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on how many people get off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it okay to film you for TV?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We are looking for the 5th place on our list of the 5 best recommended places in Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Takasaki Park is in the middle of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to go to a place like that from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is 5th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 5th in your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,1st place is Mt. Tomi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell us the 1st place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand your 1st place very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gold is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is gold in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay without clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your 5th recommended place by Kawana-san, who has lived in Iwai for 30 years and has shiny gold teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me again your 5th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He changed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- He changed it!\N- Isn't it a park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He changed it from mountain to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go there, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They immediately headed for the recommended Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone may answer that it's the Iwai Beach.\NThis might be the 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only his 5th place, but it would be in line with other people's opinions.\NThat can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That sign says Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That place is definitely famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What an old poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Isee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That one was tanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature was over 30°C (86°F) that day.\NThey were heading to Iwai Beach in the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a distance to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.\NIt's Gaki's famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"All we do is complain."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We really do complain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I watch other shows from time to time, but I have never seen any other show where the performers complain so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no one is saying that at outdoor shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All we do is complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very negative, and you have a frown on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think that needs to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog is so loud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there such a big bus parked here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there are a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a training camp for students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- The atmosphere has changed a lot.\N- I don't know if this is good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Tsukitei Housei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone!\NI'm Housei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he's Tsukitei Housei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Housei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he's Tsukitei Housei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Tsukitei Housei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Housei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this a training camp?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- What team are you guys on?\N- We are a kendo team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kendo team?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a kendo team training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call me Housei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I used to do kendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,10 minutes have passed since they started walking heading for Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.\NIt's very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- We still haven't arrived there.\N- We're not there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not yet arrived at the Iwai Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- I was sweating like a waterfall.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm going to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I could see the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where it finally starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to decide soon from 4th to 1st place too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This view isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, but there are some people.\N- There are some people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The view is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the place for those in the know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwai Beach is a 3 kilometer long arc of sandy beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a popular beach for students and parents and children who have come to a seaside school or training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So they certified Iwai Coast as the 5th recommended place near Iwai Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They then asked people who come to play at the beach to tell them the 4th recommended place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough to walk on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my feet caught in the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand is also hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature of the ground surface is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, you are at a disadvantage with those shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they from Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't think they know Iwai.\N- They would be if they weren't locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have also checked out Iwai before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not bad boys, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no such guys in such a place at such a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be scared if there were such guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're 50 years old now, right?\N- I might be robbed by that guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki had an injury on his face.\NI thought they did that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I would hate to see that happen.\N- This is a pimple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be sad if they did that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You might get your hair pulled out by them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,若いのと1 The young guys or the parasol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking at us, so we'll ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to be Iwai locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you guys locals?\N- No, we are here for a training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you guys from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you guys in the kendo team?\N- No, we play guitar and sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys going to a training camp at the beach too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, do you know any good places around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for a good place in Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the only place you guys know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you guys don't know anything about Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they locals there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- It may not be.\N- Let's ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The people under those parasols must be locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you locals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, you guys aren't?\N- Oh, they are barbecuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to ask you about good places in Iwai, but you guys are not locals, so you don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I have been coming to Iwai since I was a kid.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He is very familiar with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuura-san has been coming to Iwai for more than 30 years. What is his 4th recommendation for a good place in Iwai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your 4th best place in Iwai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, there is a observatory on Mt. Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Observatory on Mt. Tomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go there on foot, won't we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think you can get there in 20 minutes by car.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then I will go to that observatory.\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed to the Mt. Tomi observatory, which was recommended as the 4th best place around Iwai station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- What was the name of that mountain?\N- They said Mt. Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What kanji does that spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it okay that they are ranked 5th and 4th in the sea and observatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll be able to find the last three spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe these are the 1st or 2nd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These would be landmarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We could go back to Tokyo with Endo pretending to be an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are we going back already?\N- "Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"I thought this was finished already..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want gourmet food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The town is close to the sea, so there should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He was eating clams and drinking whiskey with soda, which looked delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he would let me have some, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is a peaceful town.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, you should live in a place like this all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also have a 5 years old son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He already thinks you're annoying, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a big pillar of sup$#@*.. of my fami&*$#@*..\N(I'm a big pillar of support of my family)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm a big pill$#@*.. of sup$#@*.. of my fami&*$#@*.."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The pillar was wobbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost collapsed on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I have more clothes on than you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take off your jacket!\NThat's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fashion, so I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-san, it would be really dangerous if you wear this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much less fashionable to collapse on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's lame.\NThere's nothing else that's that lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That patchwork thing is disgusting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the car went into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The roadway seems to end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a sign over there.\NIt says "To the summit of Mt. Tomi"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "mountain trail."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They walk to the observatory from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't imagine Iwai to be a place like this, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This one has shade compared to the sandy beach earlier, so it's better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was hot on the beach.\N- Yes, that one reflects the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no place to escape from the sunlight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day I went back to my parents' house to visit a grave in Minou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove past Master Kiyoshi's house, so I glanced at his house when I was waiting at a traffic light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His house is so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The fence is also very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yamazaki, you don't live in that neighborhood anymore, do you?\N- Yes, I don't live in that area anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- You lived in Minou once, didn't you?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that if you live in Minou, you will be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you broke that superstition.\N- That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,5 minutes have passed since they started to climb the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we almost there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not yet.\N- Aren't we about a third of the way up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this 4th place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Tomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no shade from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough to be in the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If that wasn't a good view, I'd shit in the field and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed for the observatory in over 30°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 4th place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- If this had been the 1st place spot, I would've tried a lot harder.\N- That would have given them a sense of accomplishment and motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- But this is 4th place.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The road is so twisty I can't see ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- How far have we climbed?\N- I can't see ahead at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are no signs telling us how much further we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes have passed since they started climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- As I keep saying, this is only 4th place.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is before we introduce 4th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My pants are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back to Osaka like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wearing soaking wet pants?\N- I certainly don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going home on the Kodama again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going home on the Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were a Kodama, it would take about 5 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That one stops at every station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard he is told by Yoshimoto to take the Kodama to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is going down the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would be stupid enough to climb up to the observatory in such a fucking hot weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sunlight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo, sing a song for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Song...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's climb
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing an existing song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's what I thought.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that fake shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Jean with the good figure and beauty I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The tempo is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes have passed since they started climbing Mt. Tomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are sweating terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei-san is sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to drink some water or you'll collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because of your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it with the jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't understand this because you're not fashionable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fashionable enough to understand what I'm feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you fashionable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you fashionable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,30 minutes have passed since they started climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seeing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-  I can't see anything ahead.\N- The road goes on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even reached the entrance, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is intense hiking!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is intense hiking in the middle of summer.\NAnd I'm wearing Crocs!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I wore shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess since we came to Iwai, we were destined to climb mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one was ranked too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish this had ranked 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it had ranked later, the sun would have set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it would have been pitch black here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it had been 35 minutes since they started their climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes 45 minutes from here to the observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's not a kilometer left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the sign earlier, "1.1 km, 20 minutes," referring to just up to here?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- It took more than 20 minutes, right?\N- Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- And if it takes 45 minutes even though it's not 1km, does that mean the road is really steep?\N- Yes, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll split up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all climb up, we will run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One of us should climb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hamada, please.
